 \left( \begin{array}{c} u+y \\ y \end{array} \right) \left( \begin{array}{c} n \\ u+y \end{array} \right) = \left( \begin{array}{c} n-y \\ u \end{array} \right) \left( \begin{array}{c} n \\ y \end{array} \right) 
\binom{u+y}{y}\binom{n}{u+y} = \frac{(u+y)!n!}{y!u!(u+y)!(n-u-y)!} =\frac{n!}{y!u!(n-u-y)!} =\\= \frac{n!}{y!(n-y)!}\frac{(n-y)!}{u!(n-u-y)!} = \binom{n}{y}\binom{n-y}{u}
 \left( \begin{array}{c} u+y \\ y \end{array} \right) \left( \begin{array}{c} n \\ u+y \end{array} \right) = \frac{(u+y)!}{u!y!} \cdot\frac{n!}{(u+y)!(n-u-y)!}= \frac{(n-y)!}{u!(n-y-u)!} \cdot\frac{n!}{y!(n-y)!}= \left( \begin{array}{c} n-y \\ u \end{array} \right) \left( \begin{array}{c} n \\ y \end{array} \right) 
